column5: I picked up a MH Compre for one reel and looking for one of the Compre crankbait rods for the other.  New stuff gives a person the itch.
your telling me!  new fly reel today and a new combo coming on the weekend.  I need SOFT WATER NOW!!!!  there, I'm done (for the night).
